title: TalkTEI Conversation Series with Levi Benton: Los Angeles,CA
desc: This is an open discussion led by Levi Benton where YOU determine the conversation. There are no stupid questions and there is absolutely no judgement. Topics will range from music to art to friendship and even daily challenges. This conversation is to help build a support system amongst the Miss May I community, so don't hold back. Grab your ticket and let's talk! ? We ask that you meet behind the venue at the white Miss May I trailer 15 minutes prior. From there Levi and/or our TEI representative will escort you into the venue for the workshop. We hope you have great experience!
